# Project Title

This project was made for the course "Drone and Autonomous Robotic System". The idea behind this project is to develope a simulation of a drone that follow autonomously a football depending on range of factors like speed and change of direction.


## Installation

The easiest way to start the project is to use Docker.
After installing Docker start the project with the following command inside the "src" folder:

```bash
sudo docker build -t josedallatorre/sjtu_drone:latest .
sudo bash run_docker.sh
```
     